# No Watermarks or Tool Branding

- Do **not** add watermarks, "Made with …", tool credits, or any similar branding to code, UI, docs, or assets.
- Do **not** make your own decision to insert such text or imagery anywhere in the project.
- Output and generated content must stay free of tool/IDE/agent attribution unless the user explicitly asks for it.